{"tid":237905,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[永恆經典]《未來戰士績集》3D版將於2017年8月25日上映","createTime":"2017-05-10T16:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T09:52:48.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a81867eb5cac10271f3b3dab2aa2496953b9c6d","tid":237905,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://moviesoon.com/news/2017/03/james-cameron-dmg-partner-for-terminator-2-3d-re-release-targeting-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoviesoon.com%2Fnews%2F2017%2F03%2Fjames-cameron-dmg-partner-for-terminator-2-3d-re-release-targeting-china%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=0e04f568\" target=\"_blank\">http://moviesoon.com/news/2017/03/james-cameron-dmg-partner-for-terminator-2-3d-re-release-targeting-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n詹姆斯&middot;卡梅隆（James Cameron）的《終結者2》（Terminator 2: Judgment Day）2017年8月25日將以3D形式在全球重映，以慶祝這部影片誕生26週年。<br />\n<br />\n此次3D轉制由DMG與StudioCanal兩家公司負責，卡梅隆也將參與。轉制的新技術​​由StereoD公司提供。<br />\n<br />\n《終結者2》1991年上映，是該系列中最成功的一部，不僅票房很高，而且還獲得了四項奧斯卡獎。然而，這部影片從來沒有在中國大陸的影院上映過。此次3D重映將彌補這一遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n卡梅隆的《泰坦尼克號》在2012年也曾被轉製成3D電影上映，當時這部影片在中國收穫了1.45億美元票房，超過美國本土的票房5780萬。而《泰坦尼克號》重映的全球總票房也達到了3.43億美元。有了這麼成功的先例，《終結者2》製作3D版也就不奇怪了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://moviesoon.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Terminator-2-t100-image_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoviesoon.com%2Fnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2FTerminator-2-t100-image_medium.jpg&h=e26e4a96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/terminator-2-3d-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Fterminator-2-3d-poster.jpg&h=3c0fe88a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6c07d30a42ac842c5bb04bf4501eab4484becee","tid":237905,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10